JWT class to create and validate JWT tokens

Setup:

- add to requirements.txt:
	ft-jwt-validation==1.0.5
- add to django settings.py INSTALLED_APPS:
	"ft_jwt_validation",

Usage:

- import the class:
	from ft_jwt_validation.jwt import JWT
